  <span id="freeText17007593757090246778" style="display:none">Seems it was quite a controversial and provocative book in its day. Dr.Moreau creates hybrid creatures through the vivisection of animals. It deals with the issues of the misuse of science,the lack of ethics and cruelty. <br /><br />But personally,I didn't find it memorable. The storytelling didn't grab my interest. <br /><br />Vivisection did,however,remind me of all those poor frogs,I was forced to dissect in Biology class.</span>
